===Format===
* '''Haier BGMI G-League 2025:'''
* '''Pre Quarter:''' ''July 10th - 11th''
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, 64 teams: divided into 4 groups
** 6 matches each day
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 12 teams}} from each group advance to ''Quarter Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em></div>
* '''Quarter Finals:''' ''July 12th - 13th''
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, 48 teams: divided into 3 groups
** 6 matches each day
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from each group advance to ''Semi Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''' ''July 14th,15th and 17th''
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, 24 teams: divided into 3 groups
** 6 matches each day
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} advance to ''Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''' ''July 18th - 21st''
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, 16 teams
** 6 matches each day
** On Day 2,teams will be awarded with {{Bgcolortext|up|additional 3 points}} for every chicken they secure.
** On Day 4,teams will earn {{Bgcolortext|up|2 points for every finish}} secured during the {{Bgcolortext|up|Stage 1 (first zone)}} of the match.
